query.querystr: stmt s; assign a; Select s such that Follows(s, (Select a))
stmt s; assign a; Select s such that Follows(s, (Select a such that Uses(a, "x")))
stmt s; assign a; Select BOOLEAN such that Follows((Select s such that Modifies(s, "x")), (Select a such that Uses(a, "x")))
stmt s; assign a; variable v; Select s such that Follows(s, (Select a such that Uses(a, (Select v such that Modifies(5, v)))))
stmt s; assign a; variable v; constant c; Select s such that Follows(s, (Select a such that Uses(a, (Select v such that Modifies((Select s with s.stmt# = c.value), v)))))

stmt s, s1; variable v1; with w1; constant ct1; assign a1, a2; call c1; Select s such that Uses(s, (Select v1 pattern w1(v1, _) such that Next(w1, s1) with s1.stmt# = ct1.value)) or Uses((Select a1 pattern a1(v1, _) such that Affects(a1, a2) such that Follows(a2, s1)), (Select v1 with c1.procName = v1.varName such that Parent*(c1, w1) such that Follows(w1, s1)))

stmt s1; variable v1; call c1,c2; assign a1; constant ct1; if ifs1; Select v1 with s1.stmt# = (Select s1 such that Parent(s1, c1) with ifs1.stmt# = c1.procName such that Parent(s1, c2)) or s1.stmt# = (Select ct1 such that Parent(a1, c1) such that Parent*(ifs1, c1) with ifs1.stmt# = ct1.value)

Select v1 pattern a((Select v1 such that Uses(a1, v1) such that Next(a1, c1) such that Next(c1, ifs1)), _) or ifs((Select v2 such that Modifies(s1, v1) such that Uses(s1, v2) such that Uses(s2, v2)), _, _)
stmt s1; variable v1; Select s1 such that Uses(s1, (Select v1 such that Modifies(2, v1)))
assign a1, a2; stmt s2; Select a1 such that Follows(a1, a2) and Parent(a1, (Select s1 such that Next*(a1, s1)))
stmt s1, s2; assign a, a2; constant c1; Select s2 such that Next*(s1, a2) pattern a("u", _) with s1.stmt# = c1.value such that Affects(s2, a2)
variable v1; stmt s1; assign a, a1; Select s1 Uses((Select s1 such that Uses(s1, v1) such that Next(a1, s1)), _)
assign a1; stmt s2; variable v1; Select a1 such that Modifies((Select a1 such that Next(1, a1)), (Select v1 such that Uses(s2, v1)))
variable v1, v2; procedure p1; assign a; Select p1 such that Modifies(p1, v1) pattern a(v1, _) such that Uses(p1, (Select v2 pattern a(v2, _)))
assign a1, a2; stmt s1; Select a1 such that Affects*(a1, (Select a2 such that Parent*(s1, a2)))
while w1; assign a2; variable v3; Select w1 such that pattern w1((Select v3 such that Uses(a2, v3)), _)
stmt s1, s2, s3; variable v1; Select <s1, s2> such that Affects((Select s1 such that Uses(s1, v1)), (Select s2 such that Next*(s2, s3)))
stmt s1, s2; variable v1; Select s2 such that Follows*((Select s1 such that Uses((Select s1 such that Modifies(s1, v1)), v2)), s2)
stmt s1, s2; variable v1; Select <s1, s2> such that Parent(s1, (Select s2 such that Uses(s2, v1)))
procedure p1; variable v2; stmt s1; Select v2 such that Modifies(p1, (Select v2 such that Uses(s1, v2)))
procedure p1; variable v2; stmt s1; Select v2 such that Modifies(p1, (Select v2 such that Uses(3, v2)))
variable v2; stmt s1; Select s1 such that Uses(s1, (Select v2 such that Uses(3, v2)))
